bib_record.title: Validation and upgrading of the recommended cross section data of charged particle reactions used for production of PET radioisotopes

free_txt: Experimental data were collected and critically
selected for each of the reactions. Recommended cross
section data set were created by using statistical fit
over the selected data. Recommended thick target yield,
physical yield or saturation yield were calculated.
